name: 30 Minutes of LAX Spotting!
description:
Hey everyone, this is a 30-minute long compilation of planes taking off and landing at Los Angeles International Airport. About 75% of this is old footage, but there's still a few new videos in there. Please note that the videos featured in this compilation are not my best videos. Visit my channel (youtube.com/dude8472productions) for better videos.

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
